Package: cbamm
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Bayesian and Advanced Meta-Analysis Methods
Version: 5.7.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mahmood", "Ahmad", email = "mahmood.ahmad@ahmadiyya.org", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1234-5678"))
    )
Description: A unified framework for advanced evidence synthesis. Implements 
    entropy-balanced transportability weighting, Hartung-Knapp-Sidik-Jonkman 
    adjustments, Bayesian model stacking, and multiverse meta-analysis. Features 
    include component network meta-analysis, one-stage IPD models, and restricted 
    cubic spline dose-response modeling. Includes a "TruthCert" reporting 
    protocol for technical audit trails and automated methodological advice.
